OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FIslanders in Guernsey are calling for
OL,8,Fthe introduction of whistleblowing
OL,9,Flaws, after a lack of protection for
OL,10,Fislanders who raise concerns at work
OL,11,Fhas been flagged.
OL,13,FThey say the lack of legal protection
OL,14,Fleaves employees vulnerable to unfair
OL,15,Frepercussions from their employers if
OL,16,Fthey flag any problems they might have
OL,17,Fin the workplace - which, in some
OL,18,Fcases, could effectively silence them.
