OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FSally says she was unsupported, and
OL,8,Fultimately forced to leave her
OL,9,Fworkplace, after flagging concerns she
OL,10,Fhad about one of her managers.
OL,12,F"We were seeing things happening (in
OL,13,Fthe workplace) that we didn't like",
OL,14,Fshe explains "and myself and a
OL,15,Fcolleague put a complaint in.
OL,17,F"The person that we complained about
OL,18,Fhad a huge promotion, and she became
OL,19,Fmy boss.
OL,26,@tD@bpmuD@Npn
