OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"I was off work for a while, and when
OL,8,FI came back I got told by a colleague
OL,9,Fto 'watch my back' because someone
OL,10,Fthat was working with me and this same
OL,11,Fmanager that I'd complained about had
OL,12,Fput in some allegations about me."
OL,14,FShe says not only was nothing done
OL,15,Fabout her original concerns, but she
OL,16,Fultimately had to hand in her notice.
OL,18,F"I could not stay there. It was an
OL,19,Fimpossible situation", she explains.
