OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FSally worked for the States of
OL,8,FGuernsey - an employer which does have
OL,9,Finternal whistleblowing policies in
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FThe policy states: "Raising concerns
OL,13,Fwhich fall within the scope of the
OL,14,FWhistleblowing Policy is strongly
OL,15,Fencouraged, rather than remaining
OL,16,Fsilent.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
