OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FWhilst she contacted the
OL,8,Forganisation's designated
OL,9,FWhistleblowing Officer, she says she
OL,10,Fwas never contacted by them throughout
OL,11,Fthe course of their investigation.
OL,13,FSally adds she has spent the past
OL,14,Fthree years feeling dismissed,
OL,15,Foverlooked, and not listened to.
OL,17,F"I feel that people have been playing
OL,18,Fme", she says.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
