OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1769526716
OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"I don't want to keep talking about
OL,8,Fthis, I don't want to keep being the
OL,9,Fperson I am at the moment.
OL,11,F"But I've got no option - because if I
OL,12,Fwalk away, something awful might
OL,13,Fhappen."
OL,15,FDeputy Rob Curgenven says he is now
OL,16,Fpushing for change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
