OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"We need them to have protection so
OL,8,Fthey can speak out", he says "because
OL,9,Fif we don't know what the issues are -
OL,10,Fand there are systemic issues in the
OL,11,FStates, I don't think anyone would
OL,12,Fdisagree with that point - but if we
OL,13,Fdon't know what they are, we can't do
OL,14,Fanything about that."
OL,16,FThe calls come as Jersey's first
OL,17,Fwhistleblowing legislation - the
OL,18,FPublic Disclosure Law - is expected to
OL,19,Fbe brought forward later this year,
OL,20,Ffollowing recommendations from the
OL,21,Fisland's Employment Forum last summer.
