OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the Public Interest
OL,8,FDisclosure Act protects has been in
OL,9,Fforce for decades in the UK.
OL,11,FGuernsey's lack of legislation means
OL,12,Fpeople such as Sally who do raise
OL,13,Fconcerns aren't protected by law
OL,14,Funless they go through employment
OL,15,Ftribunals.
OL,17,FThere's also no obligation for any of
OL,18,Ftheir concerns to be investigated by
OL,19,Fan independent body.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
