OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1769526716
OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"But sometimes they will hit on
OL,8,Fsomething that, for whatever reason,
OL,9,Fthe organisation starts to shut down
OL,10,Fthe individual."
OL,12,FShe adds laws like these would also
OL,13,Fgive employees an external body to
OL,14,Fappeal to if their internal work
OL,15,Fprocedures let them down.
OL,17,F"We've had too many instances in the
OL,18,FUK - probably in Guernsey as well -
OL,19,Fwhere things have not been addressed
OL,20,Fproperly internally", she explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/13
