OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"Then people do need the option and
OL,8,Favailability to go to the regulatory
OL,9,Fauthority and get the right
OL,10,Faccountability mechanism."
OL,12,FWhen approached by ITV News for
OL,13,Fcomment, the States of Guernsey said:
OL,14,F"While we cannot comment publicly on
OL,15,Fthe details of individual enquiries
OL,16,Ffrom the complaints or whistleblowing
OL,17,Fprocess, we are deeply thankful to
OL,18,Fthose who come forward with genuine
OL,19,Fconcerns. Their willingness to speak
OL,20,Fup helps us learn and improve.
