OL,3,CLack of whistleblowing legislation
OL,4,Cleaving islanders in Guernsey
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"The States of Guernsey is committed
OL,8,Fto maintaining the highest standards
OL,9,Fof care and operates a robust
OL,10,Fwhistleblowing policy that protects
OL,11,Fanyone raising genuine concerns in
OL,12,Fgood faith, even if those concerns are
OL,13,Flater found to be unfounded.
OL,15,FSpeaking up is strongly encouraged
OL,16,Fover staying silent, as it helps
OL,17,Fensure our services remain safe,
OL,18,Fresponsive, and accountable. The
OL,19,Fwellbeing of our staff and service
OL,20,Fusers is at the heart of everything we
OL,21,Fdo."
